Name "Nuclearcraft Alloying and Crafting - MBC"

-- Below You can Adjust the power values and Tick Timings. --
-- If you adjust Tick timings though for power, Peak Tick Time will --
-- Go up. Just be aware. --

-- Tick times on Item Distribution cannot be changed due to mod limits! --
-- Adjust Item Values as needed --

Every Tick do

    Input 16384 fe: : 
        From Power

    Output 16384 fe: : 
        To Bronze, Invar, Constantan, Electrum, Alumite, CrystaltineDust, CrystaltineIngot,
        IronAlloy, EnergeticAlloy, VibrantAlloy, ModPrimer, Modularium, PulsIron, 
        RedstoneAlloy, Brass, Soularium, EnergeticSilvAlloy, VividAlloy, DarkSteel, 
        EndSteel, ElectricalSteel, MelAlloy, DimBlend, EnergeticBlend, Steel, FerroBoron,
        ToughAlloy

End

-- Alloyer Recipes Below This Line --

-- Each Recipe is Labeled for Convenience and Organization!

-- Bronze Ingot --

Every 80 Ticks do

-- Bronze Ingot --

        Input 8
            thermalfoundation:material@129
            From EMCLink
        Input 24
            thermalfoundation:material@128
            From EMCLink

        Output Retain 8
            thermalfoundation:material@129
            To Bronze Slot 0
        Output Retain 24
            thermalfoundation:material@128
            To Bronze Slot 1

Forget

-- FerroBoron --

        Input 8
            material@160
            From Drawers
        
        Input 8
            ingot@5
            From EMCLink
    
        Output 8 Each
            Retain 8 ingot@5,
            Retain 8 material@160
            To FerroBoron

Forget

-- Tough Alloy --

        Input 8
            alloy@6
            From Drawers
        
        Input 8
            ingot@6
            From EMCLink

        Output 8 Each
            Retain 8 ingot@6,
            Retain 8 alloy@6
            To ToughAlloy

Forget

