        "projecte:item.pe_matter" with meta 1
        From EMCLink

    Output Retain 24
        "projecte:item.pe_matter" with meta 0
        To ModPrimer Slot 0
    Output Retain 8
        "projecte:item.pe_matter" with meta 1
        To ModPrimer Slot 1

Forget

